svg.source:
Title: Application Container - Install
participant AppCon participant AppMon participant Child Process
AppCon-->AppCon:Check list of applications
Note left of AppCon: Case 1.1:\n app is existing AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("remove") AppMon-->Child Process: "stop/die" signal Child Process-->AppMon: "ok" (Child death signal) Note left of AppCon: End Case 1.1
Note left of AppCon: Case 1.2:\n app is not existing AppCon-->AppCon: create app folder Note left of AppCon: End Case 1.2
AppCon-->AppCon: Copy app files in the app folder AppCon-->AppCon: Add app in list
Note left of AppCon: Case 2:\n app is runnable AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("setup") Note left of AppCon: Case 2.1:\n autostart is true AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("start") AppMon-->Child Process: fork() Note right of Child Process: execute \n app Child Process-->AppMon: "ok" AppMon-->AppCon: "ok" Note left of AppCon: End Case 2.1 Note left of AppCon: End Case 2
AppCon-->AppCon: Save application list
